==Translingual==

=== Pronunciation ===
/ ʋ /, often transliterated as v. Pronounced alone it is / ʋə /, typically between the English v and w, though dialects range almost to each end of the spectrum between v and w.
===Letter===
'''व''' (v)
#The fourth [[semivowel]] of the [[Devanagari]] script, but traditionally classified (and [[collated]]) as a consonant. Linguistically it is considered a labio-dental [[approximant]].

